  "body": "Use [yarn workspaces]() instead of lerna.\r\n\r\nPart of this means removing all `devDependencies` in the root's `package.json` and install them in each workspace that needs them. After this is done, all the scripts that explicitly use the root `node_modules` have to be updated. For example, `node ../../node_modules/typescript/bin/tsc` becomes just `tsc`.",
